cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.HC 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving the ability of a deep neural network model for Recognizing Textual Entailment (RTE) tasks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves training and fine-tuning machine learning models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it involves crowdsourcing and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as it deals with human involvement in the training process.
